701381f-a.title: Bronx: Kingsbridge Avenue - 232nd Street (West)
701381f-a.text:
Kingsbridge Ave., west side, at West 232nd Street, showing at the N.W.
and S.W. corners respectively P.S. No. 7 and a part of St. Johns Academy;
the latter being a 3-story frame building. The view is in a northerly
direction.
Ootober 27, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

701382f-a.title: Bronx: Kingsbridge Avenue - 232nd Street (West)
701382f-a.text:
3129-3133 Kingsbridge Ave., adjoining the S.W. corner of West 232nd
Street, showing the Convent of Jesus and Mary.
October 27, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
